,"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Organize Day of Week \nNotice that the days of the week are out of order. Let's fix that.","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"tripdata_v1$day_of_week <- ordered(tripdata_v1$day_of_week, levels=c(\"Sunday\", \"Monday\", \"Tuesday\", \"Wednesday\", \"Thursday\", \"Friday\", \"Saturday\"))","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2023-06-09T14:07:28.258594Z","iopub.execute_input":"2023-06-09T14:07:28.260142Z","iopub.status.idle":"2023-06-09T14:07:28.427039Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Average ride time by each day for members vs casual ","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"aggregate(tripdata_v1$ride_length ~ tripdata_v1$member_casual + tripdata_v1$day_of_week, FUN = mean)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2023-06-09T14:07:33.757661Z","iopub.execute_input":"2023-06-09T14:07:33.759207Z","iopub.status.idle":"2023-06-09T14:07:37.688132Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Analyse Ridership by type and weekday","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"aggregate(tripdata_v1$ride_length ~ tripdata_v1$member_casual + tripdata_v1$day_of_week, FUN = mean)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2023-06-09T13:51:46.259592Z","iopub.execute_input":"2023-06-09T13:51:46.261417Z","iopub.status.idle":"2023-06-09T13:51:46.284157Z"}}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Analyze ridership data by type and weekday","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"tripdata_v1 %>% \n  mutate(weekday = wday(started_at, label = TRUE)) %>%  #creates weekday field using wday()\n  group_by(member_casual, weekday) %>%  #groups by usertype member_casual and weekday\n  summarise(number_of_rides = n() #calculates the number of rides and average duration \n            ,average_duration = mean(ride_length)) %>%  # calculates the average duration\n  arrange(member_casual, weekday) # sorts","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2023-06-09T14:07:50.901503Z","iopub.execute_input":"2023-06-09T14:07:50.903134Z","iopub.status.idle":"2023-06-09T14:07:57.063398Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## Download Summary file for Visualization in Tableau","metadata":{}}]}